						               													<description>DUELS &amp;quot;au temps de la Grande Peste&amp;quot; is a simple skirmish miniature wargame that allows 2, 3, 4 or 5 players to compete to recognize their rights to the loot of an honest plunder. &amp;#10;Each lord accompanied by a loyal captain and 9 warriors will have to implement a subtle strategy to get hold of the wealth scattered on a table of 1.20 m on the side.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The goal of the game is to control the maximum amount of loot at the end of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each session is played in four fixed turns at the end of which the victory points are calculated.&amp;#10;Player start by placing peasants and loot on the table. &amp;#10;Depending on the initiative of your troop, you will choose your table edge. The last to choose his edge of the table will be the first to deploy but the first one to play in each turn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
